  @FunctionalRequirements_f371a5aa = N'- Display 5 key metrics: Pipeline Value, Active Deals, Win Rate, Avg Deal Size, Avg Cycle Time
- Make Pipeline Value, Active Deals, and Win Rate cards clickable
